     In order to set up this multi architecture system for use the very
     first time, you need to go to this directory, and type

make

     Then, put the following line in your .cshrc file (or type it at prompt)

source  this_dir/cshrc.csh

     where "this_dir" is replaced with the full path to this directory,
     and the following line in each of your Makefiles (with no indentation):

include $(ARCH_MAKEFILE)

     For an example, then cd to Example
